data.description: Beautiful two-story pool home in the private and quiet Arlington community inside Pine Lakes subdivision in desired Palm Coast. This spacious home is set on an oversized lot with a 2 car garage. Large first floor master bedroom with three bedrooms upstairs that also includes an open area that overlooks the living area downstairs and entry way. The kitchen includes stainless steel appliances and a breakfast nook. The sliding glass doors in the living room lead you out to the screened in porch where you can relax poolside or jump into the pool to cool off on those hot summer days. Conveniently located close to shopping, schools, churches, and Town Center. Don't miss out on this must see great buy, it wont last long! Previous buyer backed out because of Dog restrictions from the HOA, 2 dogs allowed per HOA. All inspections have been done and pool leak has been repaired, ready for a new buyer!
